ofcprobe.vswitch.connection

Interface IOFConnection

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OFConnection1_zero

    public interface IOFConnection
    Interface for all ofSwitch Implementations. This is the current Set of required Methods per Implementation. Basically Handles the OFMessages for a TCPSocket
    Author:
    Christopher Metter
